<body>
<canvas id="mainCanvas"></canvas>
<div id="loadingScreen">
  <div class="load-title">大庚剑阵<br>DA GENG SWORD FORMATION</div>
  <div class="load-bar-wrap"><div class="load-bar" id="loadBar"></div></div>
  <div class="load-msg" id="loadMsg">加载剑阵阵法...</div>
</div>
<div id="permScreen">
  <div class="perm-icon">📷</div>
  <div class="perm-title">请开启摄像头权限</div>
  <div class="perm-desc">通过手势结印催动大庚剑阵，所有运算均在本地完成，不会上传任何数据</div>
